Install Python , Ex - Vscode
Install Local MySql Server, Ex -XAMPP
Run Both Applications Vscode & XAMPP Server 
In XAMPP You need to ON MySql & Apache Server
In Xampp Control Panel you need to note down the port no. Ex- Default port - 3360
Default User = "root" but you need to Set Password " "
Now, Copy Repository connect.py file (Start from import mysql.connector as connection)
paste it in VScode Editor 
save and run in the Terminal of VScode.
